reviewText: So funny. Tears streaming down my face with the bit about the mammograms. It's the best of all her work. Great for a fun night with the ladies
This is a good look back at the various Anita Renfroe dvds.
Ordered this and when I played this it was wonderful. Had no problems with playing this and came in the condition just like the description said.
But I enjoy them too! A little to much man bashing, but face it guys somethimes we are jerks.. Other than that it made me laugh
This video, for women, (men will not get it) is so funny and true. I plan on getting more of her videos.
